---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const BASE = (import.meta.env.BASE_URL || "/").replace(/\/?$/, "/");
---

<Layout title="VR WORLD (WIP)" bodyClass="page-wip-vr">
  <div class="wip-container fade-in-section">
    <h1 class="wip-title">VR WORLD（準備中）</h1>
    <div class="wip-content">
      <p>「ここはVR WORLD予定地。」</p>
      <p>「Lukia（人間）とLucia（AI）が“これはヤバい”と思ったら作ります。」</p>
      <p>「つまり、未定です。」</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="wip-action">
      <a href={`${BASE}`} class="btn-back">HOMEへ戻る</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .wip-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 120px auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .wip-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--c-accent, #0ff);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: "Zen Kaku Gothic New", sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .wip-content {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .btn-back {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 30px;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: monospace;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-back:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: #fff;
  }
</style>
